description:
GNOME 46.5 is now available as the fifth maintenance update to the GNOME 46 desktop environment series with more bug fixes and improvements. Here's what's changed since GNOME 46.4.

The post GNOME 46.5 Released with Mutter and GNOME Shell Improvements appeared first on 9to5Linux - do not reproduce this article without permission. This RSS feed is intended for readers, not scrapers.
title: GNOME 46.5 Released with Mutter and GNOME Shell Improvements
